    {
      "chinese": "開工之前，長老必然依俗作法。以竹籤或樹枝串起肉、魚、滋粑，並以自釀香醇的糯米酒揮向天灑在地，簡單誠懇敬天拜地，祈願老天爺與祖靈庇佑風調雨順，國泰民安，工作順利，平安豐收。",
      "ab": "pa’naaring sumiatu’ ga, galgan cubalay na nabakis ku Gaga’. sipalhu ca tinagaq na buwiqa’ quga raqni’ na kahuneq ku siyam, quleh, tinabeq, sighap tagi kaal sipqusiya’ ca rawq ku quwaw mingilis tumubun cu ginualu’ ni Yaba’ Utux na Kaal ru Nanabakis, muwa’ na balayq a kaal, manbalbalayq i maqiyanux kahabaag ku itaal i makababaw na rawq, ini’ luwag cu aqeh i matawwaw ru payux a kinloh.",
